text: Kleinwallstadt is a market community in the Miltenberg district in the region of Lower Franconia in Bavaria, Germany and the seat of the Administrative Community. == Geography == === Place === Kleinwallstadt is in the Bavarian Lower Main (Bayerischer Untermain) Region.
